---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="How it works — One Run Travel Packages">
  <Nav />
  <section style="padding:160px 48px 80px;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-tag">Process</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:32px;">How it <em>works</em></h2>
    <div style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.9;color:rgba(243,239,232,0.65);">
      <div style="margin-bottom:48px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;color:#f3efe8;margin:0 0 12px;">1. Pick your race</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--mute);">Browse our collection of hand-picked races across Greece. From the historic Athens Marathon to the scenic trails of Crete, each event has been chosen for its unique character and runner experience. Filter by distance, month, or status to find the perfect race for your next running adventure.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom:48px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;color:#f3efe8;margin:0 0 12px;">2. Choose your hotel &amp; package</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--mute);">Each race comes with carefully selected hotel partners &mdash; from boutique city stays to beachfront resorts. Pick the hotel and room type that suits your style and budget. Every package includes race entry, accommodation, and local transfers, so all you need to do is pack your running shoes.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom:48px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;color:#f3efe8;margin:0 0 12px;">3. Register &amp; pay</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--mute);">Fill in your runner details &mdash; name, nationality, emergency contact, and any medical notes we should know about. Upload your medical certificate if the race requires one. Pay securely by bank transfer to our Greek account (Alpha Bank). Once we confirm your payment, you&rsquo;re in.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom:48px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:500;color:#f3efe8;margin:0 0 12px;">4. Show up &amp; run</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--mute);">Arrive in Greece, check into your hotel, collect your race bib, and run. We handle the logistics so you can focus on the race. Our team is available on the ground during race weekend to help with anything you need &mdash; from last-minute questions to restaurant recommendations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Base>
